	   <tr><td colspan=2>Clan Werre on FV took CT out just this last weekend.&nbsp;&nbsp;He starts with ~200 to 300K HP and regens ~2K a tick.  So look for a long fight, took us about 15 min to drop him.  Look at bringing the DPS to do ~500K or dont go at all.  <br><br>As for the DT every one thinks he has, nope.  In 15 min he did not DT one time.  And our MT got to use her disc two times.<br><br>As for this robe .... WE GOT 3 OF THEM =)<br><br>Aaeb Soulblade<br>Holy Knight of Clan Werre<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
